{
  "stem": "18932.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- yeah, I have two grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have Rachel and I have Brooke, which is two and a half, and Rachel is 11.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my-- my son-- my daughter is a-- you want to know what they do or you don't?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My daughter is a psychiatric social worker, but now she's with the school-- board of education, and my son is a doctor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He's a psychiatrist, but right now he's working for a pharmaceutical company.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And thank god we survived, and we're here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just destiny.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just-- I had-- we had years to live, and we lived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I strongly believe in whatever is destined for you, that's what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to be in the right place at the right time, and you have to be lucky.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You have to educate people, to tell them what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It should never happen again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it can happen to anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not only the Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Another time, they might pick another, you know, another race, another religion and-- and say you decided this is not good and this is not right.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's why people have to be educated to know that everybody is-- is equal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody is a person.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody has a right to live and to exist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm afraid now?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes when I read the paper and I see what's happening, I-- I-- I fear that, God forbid, could-- could happen again.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I hope to God it won't, that people should hear and-- and-- and learn of whatever happened in the past and should learn from it and be more tolerant of other people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because, you know, you never know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You never know what-- what's coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're welcome.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
